text: Olgovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Rassvetovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Davlekanovo, 5 km from Rassvet. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Olgovka
